"""
        Test that a TypeError is raised when an invalid value is used to set
        the DRBG algorithm of an RNGParameters structure.
        """
kwargs = {'drbg_algorithm': 'invalid'}
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The DRBG algorithm must be a DRBGAlgorithm enumeration.', objects.
    RNGParameters, **kwargs)
args = objects.RNGParameters(), 'drbg_algorithm', 'invalid'
self.assertRaisesRegex(TypeError,
    'The DRBG algorithm must be a DRBGAlgorithm enumeration.', setattr, *args)
